            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Buffalo</placeName>
                <add>?</add>
                <add>?</add>
                <date>Tebetta 5613</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Revd Mr</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <addressee>Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>
                    <hi rend="underline">Phila. Pa</hi>
                </placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I find myself duty bound, to address<lb/> a few lines to you, on
                account of our Holy<lb/> Religion. I heard this week, that the Learned<lb/>
                <persName>Revd Mr R. J. Fürstenthal</persName> from <placeName><hi rend="underline"
                        >Breslaw</hi></placeName>, has trans„<lb/>lated, the valuable Book,
                    <add>חובת הלבבות</add>, from the<lb/> Hebrew, in the <hi rend="underline">High
                    German Language</hi>. I would<lb/> advise you, to take upon you the<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">Task</hi> and translate, only the first<lb/> Chapter, and I
                    <add>am</add> certain <del>and</del> that such<lb/> small pamphlet, will be
                taken by all our<lb/> Bretheren, Israelites, and Gentiles.</p>
            <p>on account of the <add>גט</add>
                <sic>wich</sic> you <hi rend="underline">recd</hi><lb/> the letters from me, you
                will be so good<lb/> could <del>have p</del>
                <add>?</add>, <sic>untill</sic> next month,<lb/> because it will proved by a <hi
                    rend="underline">Justice</hi> of<lb/> the <hi rend="underline">Peacex</hi>, if
                such <hi rend="underline">Divorce</hi> was <hi rend="underline">given</hi>.
                    <persName>Mr <hi rend="underline">Noah</hi></persName> did not,
                    <sic>answers</sic> me at present, if<lb/> he will take the <hi rend="underline"
                    >bible</hi> with English, the spelling<lb/> Book He recd from
                    <persName>Ignausse</persName>, but with prayer<lb/> Books is He provided on
                both. <add>מנהגים</add></p>
            <p>I recd <sic>a</sic> answer from <placeName>Mobile</placeName>, very <hi
                    rend="underline">favourable</hi><lb/> not as a <hi rend="underline"
                    >preacher</hi>
                <add>but</add> for some other <hi rend="underline">Branches</hi><lb/> in our
                Religion at present I have no more<lb/> to communicate to you</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">I Remain Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">your friend and <add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">I am <persName role="author">M. Plutery</persName></p>
            <p>my <sic>bes</sic> respet<add>?</add> to the Mr</p>
            <p><persName>Joseph Ash</persName>, <add>א</add></p>
            <p>his families and<add>?</add> relations</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><add>?</add>my <sic>adress</sic> you</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">know</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
